<F P=100> Egypt </F>
<H3> <TI>   Musa Considers Libyan Request for Forces in Aouzou </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  NC1503145394 Cairo MENA in Arabic 1430 GMT 15 Mar 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC1503145394 </F>
<F P=104>  Cairo MENA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Cairo, 15 Mar (MENA)--Foreign Minister 'Amr Musa has 
stated that the Libyan request to send Egyptian forces to the 
Aouzou Strip to supervise the Libyan withdrawal from the region 
and their handing it over to the Chadian authorities is 
currently under consideration. Commenting on this issue today, 
he said that a decision will be made proceeding from Egypt's 
chairmanship of the OAU. 

</TEXT>

