<H3> <TI>   Arrest of Ba'labakk Demonstrators Ordered </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  NC1503122794 Beirut Radio Lebanon in Arabic 1130 GMT 15 Mar 
94 </F>

<F P=103> NC1503122794 </F>
<F P=104>  Beirut Radio Lebanon </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The government representative at the military court 
has instructed all security services to look for those who 
paraded with weapons in Ba'labakk on 11 March immediately. The 
security services have been instructed to arrest the 
demonstrators and refer them to the military court. 
  The government representative added: If this is not 
possible, the security services should prepare a statement on 
the identity and place of residence of the demonstrators and 
another statement that could assist the investigations. 

</TEXT>

