<F P=101> India </F>
<H3> <TI>   Demonstrators Present Petition at U.S. Embassy </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  BK1503160694 Delhi All India Radio Network in English 1430 
GMT 15 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> BK1503160694 </F>
<F P=104>  Delhi All India Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] A demonstration was held outside the American 
Embassy in New Delhi today to protest against the U.S. 
Government's policy to support the terrorist activities of 
Pakistan in Jammu and Kashmir. The demonstrators led by a 
former minister and chairman of Rashtriya Ekta Nirman Shakti, 
Mr. Anil Shastri, handed over a memorandum to the embassy which 
called for noninterference in India's internal affairs and 
stopping support to Pakistan for its terrorist activities in 
India. 

</TEXT>

