<DOCNO> FBIS3-13593 </DOCNO>
<HT>    "drnes051_k_94001" </HT>


<HEADER>
<AU>   FBIS-NES-94-051 </AU>
Document Type:Daily Report 
<DATE1>  15 Mar 1994 </DATE1>

