Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] This morning, New York time, Deputy Prime Minister 
Tariq 'Aziz met with UN Security Council President Jean-Bernard 
Merimee, the French ambassador to the United Nations. After a 
one-hour and fifteen minutes meeting, Tariq 'Aziz said his 
