<H3> <TI>   Judge Issues Warrants for Suspected Church Bombers </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  NC1803105994 Shanayh Voice of the Mountain in Arabic 1000 
GMT 18 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> NC1803105994 </F>
<F P=104>  Shanayh Voice of the Mountain </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Judge Joseph Furayhah, the judicial investigator in 
the bombing of the Sayyidat al-Najat Church, has received the 
results of the investigation into the case. After questioning 
the suspects who are in custody, Judge Furayhah issued detention 
warrants against some and arrest warrants against fugitives on 
charges of participating in the operation. The security 
agencies have been instructed to pursue and arrest the fugitives. 
  Security and judicial sources have declined to reveal the 
names and number of the detained and wanted suspects to preserve 
the confidentiality of the investigation and the arrests. 

