<F P=102>  BK1803110294 Islamabad Radio Pakistan Overseas Service in 
English 0800 GMT 18 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> BK1803110294 </F>
<F P=104>  Islamabad Radio Pakistan Overseas Service </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] A contingent of Pakistani troops returned home this 
morning after completion of its tenure with the United Nations 
Peacekeeping Force in Somalia. Another battalion of the Pakistan 
Army has replaced the troops with the UN Peacekeeping Force. 
Pakistani troops are performing peacekeeping duties for over a 
year to bring peace and normalcy back in Somalia where law and 
order had totally collapsed due to civil war. 

