<F P=100> Palestinian Affairs </F>
<H3> <TI>   PLO Welcomes UN Security Council Resolution 904 </TI></H3>
<H4>   Ghawshah: Resolution `Political' Support </H4>
<F P=102> JN1903071294 Paris Radio Monte Carlo in Arabic 0615 GMT 19 
Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> JN1903071294 </F>
<F P=104>  Paris Radio Monte Carlo </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] In the first Palestinian reaction to UN Security 
Council Resolution No. 904, PLO Executive Committee member Samir 
Ghawshah has stated that the resolution constitutes moral and 
political support for the Palestinian people. Ghawshah said 
that the Palestinian people would like to see the practical 
effects of this resolution ensure the restoration of the 
credibility of the peace march and a return to negotiations. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

